WEBVTT

1
01:39:08.000 --> 01:39:09.330 
火堆边上...
This fire...

2
01:39:10.140 --> 01:39:11.690 
也不觉得暖和
don't give much heat.

3
01:39:17.440 --> 01:39:18.810 
良心
Conscience.

4
01:39:20.250 --> 01:39:21.510 
良心是什么
What a thing.

5
01:39:23.680 --> 01:39:25.530 
要是你相信你有良心
If you believe you've got a conscience,

6
01:39:25.530 --> 01:39:27.020 
你会被他纠缠到死
it'll pester you to death.

7
01:39:27.090 --> 01:39:29.920 
但是如果你觉得你没有良心...
But if you don't believe you've got one...

8
01:39:30.090 --> 01:39:31.890 
它能把你怎么样
what can it do to you?

9
01:39:32.630 --> 01:39:36.720 
这些废话让我觉得恶心
Makes me sick all this talking and fussing about nonsense.

